{"original_text": "学校的最重要职能是培养人才。 //@真妮花的愛: //@全震动: //@嫩娃娃阿良: 转发微博", "evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1985499101", "dep": 0, "text": "学校的最重要职能是培养人才。 ", "pid": "", "tr": 41, "mid": "3622352757665393", "times": 1, "childnum": 8, "t": 1379119660, "totalChildren": 41, "dr": 8, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1426361853", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622352757665393", "tr": 1, "mid": "3622354275548663", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379120022, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1885227752", "dep": 0, "text": "[鼓掌]为战斗在教学第一线的老师鼓掌", "pid": "3622354275548663", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622366959536413", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379123045, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "From_Sara_With_Love"}], "name": "张文强-复旦"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1700864984", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622352757665393", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622356503424277", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379120553, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "davidce"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1053252821", "dep": 0, "text": "学校作秀的广告效应真不错，浙大的教师没有科研经费什么都别想，教学是底层人的工作。 ", "pid": "3622352757665393", "tr": 5, "mid": "3622358336568879", "times": 1, "childnum": 2, "t": 1379120990, "totalChildren": 5, "dr": 2, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2075315403", "dep": 0, "text": "这二位教师科研上也不赖呀，浙大用不着也不会为这作秀，这是段永平校友捐赠设立此奖的一份心意，一种鼓舞！ ", "pid": "3622358336568879", "tr": 3, "mid": "3622401483471077", "times": 1, "childnum": 2, "t": 1379131276, "totalChildren": 3, "dr": 2, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1053252821", "dep": 0, "text": "高校对教学的重视是说得多做得少，对科研是做得多说得少。如果在评价考核机制上真正将它们平等对待了，那才是把教学的重视落到了实处。当然奖教金有比没有好，获奖的老师是令人尊敬的。", "pid": "3622401483471077", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622460849318756", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379145431, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "浙大彭韧"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1870422587", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622401483471077", "tr": 1, "mid": "3622494008772890", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379153336, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1084843043", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622494008772890", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622498836715610", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379154489, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "fighting莫儿"}], "name": "浙江大学金海燕"}], "name": "boywen_zju"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2196773392", "dep": 0, "text": "张老师的科研可是做得很牛逼的", "pid": "3622358336568879", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622765628042009", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379218096, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "我被冬天摸了一下屌"}], "name": "浙大彭韧"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1774395687", "dep": 0, "text": "Agreed", "pid": "3622352757665393", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622369308016625", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379123606, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "黄瓜皮_SCU"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2747537864", "dep": 0, "text": "@骁勇zju ", "pid": "3622352757665393", "tr": 3, "mid": "3622381878705079", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379126603, "totalChildren": 3, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1928952043", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622381878705079", "tr": 2, "mid": "3622385334525253", "times": 1, "childnum": 2, "t": 1379127426, "totalChildren": 2, "dr": 2, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1543580155", "dep": 0, "text": "让我想起了费曼的随笔《教授的尊严》！", "pid": "3622385334525253", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622403353302242", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379131722, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "刘佳伟OL"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2988755942", "dep": 0, "text": "真希望我们学校也能搞个这样的比赛", "pid": "3622385334525253", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622416201260991", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379134785, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "xiaopai501"}], "name": "1024空明流转"}], "name": "Xiaog_Han"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1914339764", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622352757665393", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622382839032726", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379126832, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "unicode-章"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1685802410", "dep": 0, "text": "要从制度上扭转这种不重视教学的局面，而不是简单的给个别人奖励。e.g.,职称评定不要SCI，要课程上座率。。", "pid": "3622352757665393", "tr": 22, "mid": "3622387125789689", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379127854, "totalChildren": 22, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1985499101", "dep": 0, "text": "但是完全否定大学的研究方面也是偏颇。研究型大学的科研工作本身就是一种人才的培养。学校的教育不是只体现在课堂上课。 ", "pid": "3622387125789689", "tr": 21, "mid": "3622408705050867", "times": 1, "childnum": 5, "t": 1379132999, "totalChildren": 21, "dr": 5, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1613053290", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622408705050867", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622411712908260", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379133716, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "码喵"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1615041123", "dep": 0, "text": " ", "pid": "3622408705050867", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622413335819988", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379134103, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "aawoo"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1807089157", "dep": 0, "text": "应鼓励研究做的好的人多做基础教育，而不是割裂，分治，我觉得没有高水平的研究培养不出高水平的人才", "pid": "3622408705050867", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622428922493312", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379137819, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "HFLYU"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1985499101", "dep": 0, "text": "回复@山东工商学院白建磊:从一个极端到另外一个极端都是不可取的。 ", "pid": "3622408705050867", "tr": 2, "mid": "3622429798442116", "times": 1, "childnum": 2, "t": 1379138028, "totalChildren": 2, "dr": 2, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1254171681", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622429798442116", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622431132967668", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379138346, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "Revive"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1242799570", "dep": 0, "text": "这个问题觉得很多人认识不清楚，对于一个研究导向的大学的教师而言。教学是必要条件，科研是充分条件。一个教师必须要上课，并且足够好；但是仅上课好并不能保证成为一个优秀教授，做大学教授必须科研突出。当然，浙大之举措，多少反映了现实之无奈，就像我们说一个官员不贪就是好官要奖励一样。", "pid": "3622429798442116", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622437637795510", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379139895, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "刘瑜_北大GISer"}], "name": "晓如微博"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1012586492", "dep": 0, "text": "大学从本质上讲就是老师和学生一起讨论和研究,将大学等同于上课的观点对于培养人是极其有害的.@晓如微博: 学校的最重要职能是培养人才。", "pid": "3622408705050867", "tr": 14, "mid": "3622431665040875", "times": 1, "childnum": 3, "t": 1379138473, "totalChildren": 14, "dr": 3, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1896824410", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622431665040875", "tr": 5, "mid": "3622478850887220", "times": 1, "childnum": 5, "t": 1379149723, "totalChildren": 5, "dr": 5, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2250363200", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622478850887220", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622480755737848", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379150177, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "欧宝欧宝"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2134104764", "dep": 0, "text": "深以为然！现在很多TOP的大学并不缺乏优秀的Researcher，但很多称不上优秀的Lecturer。", "pid": "3622478850887220", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622482890092223", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379150685, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "OM_Yuan"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2133722767", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622478850887220", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622486178696813", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379151470, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "hucm-act"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2158391734", "dep": 0, "text": "国内很多老师上课相当不错。 ", "pid": "3622478850887220", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622547046726287", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379165982, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "谭平_西门飞沙"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2506143600", "dep": 0, "text": "赞，教学与科研理应相得益彰 ", "pid": "3622478850887220", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622563386805125", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379169878, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "何军-sdufe"}], "name": "陈宝权"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1452896611", "dep": 0, "text": "我们一直认为教育就是传授知识，结果我们的学生'知识'很多，甚至背上知识的包袱，缺乏创新。 ", "pid": "3622431665040875", "tr": 1, "mid": "3622510991754351", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379157386, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1452896611", "dep": 0, "text": "实际上传授知识本身没太大错误，但我们往往教的是硬知识，应该更多给学生认识客观世界的软知识 ", "pid": "3622510991754351", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622511981438963", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379157622, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "余力RUC"}], "name": "余力RUC"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1909977582", "dep": 0, "text": "中国大学老师的三件事情：教学，科研和知心姐姐。 ", "pid": "3622431665040875", "tr": 5, "mid": "3622698703637486", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379202140, "totalChildren": 5, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1012586492", "dep": 0, "text": "总结得很全面", "pid": "3622698703637486", "tr": 4, "mid": "3622717586522524", "times": 1, "childnum": 3, "t": 1379206642, "totalChildren": 4, "dr": 3, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2025715944", "dep": 0, "text": "[哈哈][哈哈]", "pid": "3622717586522524", "tr": 1, "mid": "3622721038933269", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379207465, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2842968727", "dep": 0, "text": "@程天元不再成天玩 浙大果然富有", "pid": "3622721038933269", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622835853268083", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379234837, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "梦寻西京"}], "name": "PekingAI"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1967630931", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622717586522524", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622723219373934", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379207985, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "杨春明-SWUST"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2510237220", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622717586522524", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622750494710660", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379214488, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "zjtang_gxnu"}], "name": "CSDuyong"}], "name": "潘翔-感受生活的快乐"}], "name": "CSDuyong"}], "name": "晓如微博"}], "name": "Capt_Kevin"}, {"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1874260713", "dep": 0, "text": "学校的根本任务是人才培养，创新人才的培养离不开科研项目。将科研与教学对立的思想是极端错误的。 ", "pid": "3622352757665393", "tr": 2, "mid": "3622414967179508", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379134493, "totalChildren": 2, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "2690909703", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622414967179508", "tr": 1, "mid": "3622593095226710", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1379176961, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1905], "uid": "1888861705", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3622593095226710", "tr": 0, "mid": "3622689195272366", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1379199873, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "张梅山"}], "name": "朱慕华-东北大学"}], "name": "齐浩亮"}], "name": "晓如微博"}